1 This is the first project to tokenize people, specifically celebrities.

2 It starts with tennis and football verticals. At later stages, it will utilize a shared infrastructure and launch the 
new verticals (poker, basketball, hockey; cinema actors, models, musicians). The football GOAL token sale is 
conducted simultaneously; please see the football white paper here. 

