2.4. Current Sources of Funding

These are the current funding options for young and up-and-coming players:

• Parents’ money

• Loans from friends and donors (as traditional bank loans are hard to obtain)

• Grants from Talent Management Agencies like IMG

• National tennis federation grants, which are usually small



 

